query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 0
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('applet',
'copy',
'dns',
'google-bigquery',
'group-by',
'image-processing',
'mongodb',
'playframework',
'rails-activerecord',
'sql-server-2008',
'templates',
'twilio');
